{"tid":1811831,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"咬甩趙家賢耳廓、刺傷途人疑兇遇襲　郵差據報自首准保釋　重案組跟進","createTime":"2020-01-05T05:09:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-05T17:34:11.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"dcc80a4de23e21702f79e0c03ed933ed9073daee","tid":1811831,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T05:09:53.000Z","msg":"去年11月3日，太古城中心外發生持刀傷人事件，民主黨區議員趙家賢左耳耳殼被咬至脫落，在場人士有人圍毆疑兇 &mdash; 48 歲男子陳真。據《明報》報道，一名郵差於 1月 2 日向警方自首，他涉嫌有份襲擊疑兇陳真，獲准保釋候查。<br />\n<br />\n警方於 1 月 2 日持法庭搜查令到中央郵件中心，並在該名郵差的儲物櫃蒐證，該名郵差於同日到柴灣警署自首。東區警區重案組跟進案件。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述香港郵政證實，一名郵差日前於非執勤期間在非辦公地點被警方拘捕，又指，如公務員被裁定干犯刑事罪行，政府會按既定程序採取行動，包括紀律處分。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/涉襲擊咬甩趙家賢耳殼刺傷途人疑兇-郵差自首准保釋-重案組跟進/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%B6%89%E8%A5%B2%E6%93%8A%E5%92%AC%E7%94%A9%E8%B6%99%E5%AE%B6%E8%B3%A2%E8%80%B3%E6%AE%BC%E5%88%BA%E5%82%B7%E9%80%94%E4%BA%BA%E7%96%91%E5%85%87-%E9%83%B5%E5%B7%AE%E8%87%AA%E9%A6%96%E5%87%86%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B-%E9%87%8D%E6%A1%88%E7%B5%84%E8%B7%9F%E9%80%B2%2F&d=x%2FFuRRgY0RqQB1T9iHKuLU6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=e3dc272e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%B6%89%E8%A5%B2%E6%93%8A%E5%92%AC%E7%94%A9%E8%B6%99%E5%AE%B6%E8%B3%A2%E8%80%B3%E6%AE%BC%E5%88%BA%E5%82%B7%E9%80%94%E4%BA%BA%E7%96%91%E5%85%87-%E9%83%B5%E5%B7%AE%E8%87%AA%E9%A6%96%E5%87%86%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B-%E9%87%8D%E6%A1%88%E7%B5%84%E8%B7%9F%E9%80%B2%2F&h=89c92637\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/涉襲擊咬甩趙家賢耳殼刺傷途人疑兇-郵差自首准保釋-重案組跟進/</a>"},{"pid":"7344ff546b7a9b0f31d6fd1214523bc7e8c45b89","tid":1811831,"uid":188374,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T05:11:15.000Z","msg":"on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cde8b192cc7874806c29a38f6cc6e1de3221c4e9","tid":1811831,"